  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 631924731904
    m_Localized: Thomas Newman
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 793313161216
    m_Localized: Dr. Jane Horak
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1738969329664
    m_Localized: "That find of yours \u2013 you need to report it!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1749543170048
    m_Localized: "Hey!\r\n\r\nGot the photos you sent \u2013 what a piece! I don't
      know about you, but it looks pretty interesting to me. You don't just stumble
      across stuff like that on your own land every day.\r\n\r\nYou should definitely
      report it to the Archaeological Institute \u2013 I know it sounds like a hassle,
      but it's worth it. They'll take a look and tell you more.\r\n\r\nBy the way,
      I left a few books in your research lab that I had lying around. Might come
      in handy when you're trying to identify things.\r\n\r\nLet me know how it goes!\r\n\r\nThomas"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1470215106560
    m_Localized: "Re: Find report \u2013 confirmation of receipt"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1475617370112
    m_Localized: "Dear Sir/Madam,\r\n\r\nThank you for reporting your find. The object
      you described caught our attention \u2013 pieces from this period are relatively
      rare in the region.\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in closer cooperation, it
      would be very helpful if you could provide more details about the circumstances
      of the find and possibly formulate a hypothesis about the site. The more information
      we have, the more accurate conclusions we can draw.\r\n\r\nAs a starting point,
      I recommend studying the Chronicle of Blatn\xE1 \u2013 you should have access
      to the archive in your research lab. It may tell you more about the history
      of the area.\r\n\r\nKind regards,\r\nDr. Jana Hor\xE1kov\xE1\r\nArchaeological
      Institute"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1482949013504
    m_Localized: "Collaborator status granted \u2013 survey permission"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1734787608576
    m_Localized: "Dear Sir/Madam,\r\n\r\nIt is my pleasure to inform you that, based
      on your hypothesis, we are granting you the status of Collaborator of the Archaeological
      Institute.\r\n\r\nYour hypothesis about the site is very interesting and we
      would like to investigate it further. We are therefore granting you permission
      to conduct a metal detector survey in polygon C3.\r\n\r\nPlease update your
      interactive map \u2013 the permission has been entered into the system, but
      without your update the area will not appear as accessible.\r\n\r\nWe look
      forward to the results of your survey!\r\n\r\nKind regards,\r\nDr. Jana Hor\xE1kov\xE1\r\nArchaeological
      Institute"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
